msgstr "연결 관리"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:2585
msgid "Disconnect"
msgstr "연결 끊기"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:2594
msgid "Show tokens for debugging"
msgstr "디버깅을 위한 토큰 표시"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:2600
msgid ""
"Token fields for debugging purposes. These are automatically managed by the "
"OAuth connection."
msgstr "디버깅 목적을 위한 토큰 필드입니다. 이들은 OAuth 연결에 의해 자동으로 관리됩니다."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:2605
#: includes/crms/convertfox/admin/class-admin.php:63
#: includes/crms/customerly/admin/class-admin.php:64
